public abstract class ExtractorWorker<EC,LC>
extends javax.swing.SwingWorker<LC,java.lang.Void>

A worker thread that extracts the data from a file and generates and returns a list of data. The first generic parameter EC is the subtype of Extractor. The second generic parameter is the type of list of data. The generateList() method has to be implemented to specify how to generate the data list from the Extractor The doAtTheEnd() method has to be implemented to specify what to do at the end of the loading.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Julien Lajugie
